      "text": "Stabbeem/ peezdesmits Ohleſchn bija winna Garrums/ un weenu trihsdefimits Ohleſchu winna Plattums/ un wehl weenu Preekſch-Nammu ſchim pretti/ ir tee Stabbi ar teem reſneem Balkeem bija winneem pretti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Wiſch darrija arridsan weennu Preekſch-Nammu/ preekſch Sohda-Krehſla/ kur ta Teefa turreta ktuä/ par weennu Teefaſchanas Preekſch-Nammu taiſſja wiſch/ un apſitte to ar Zee-dreem/ no tahs Grihdes lihds Greesteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un (pee) fawa Namma/ fur wiſch dſihwoja/ bija weens zitts Pagalins Eekſchpuﬀê pee ta Preekſch-Namma/ ta patt ka tas ohtre Darbs darrihts. Un wiſch darrija Waräus Meitat/ fo Salamans bij apnehmis twee-nu Namnu/ lihds ka to Preekſch-Nammu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Wiſtas ſchahs Leetas bija no dahrguem Akmiſeem pehz Mehra zirſteem/ un abbejäs Malläs ar Sahgeem ſahgeteen/ no teem Pamatteem lihds Jum-tam/ un Ahrapuﬀê lihdſtam lee-lam Pagalnam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un tee Gruntes-Akminti btja arri ſeeli dahrgi Akminti/ no desmits Ohlektim/ un no aston Ohlektim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un uſ teem btja dahrgi pehz Mehra iſzirſti Akminti/ un Zeedra-Rohkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Bet tam leelam Pagal-mann bija wiſſapkahtt trihs Rin-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "das iſzirstu Akmiſu/ un weena Rinda no Zeedru Balkeem/ ta patt bija arri ta KUNGA Nam-ma Pagalins/ un ta paſcha Namma Preekſch-Nams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Un tas Kehniſch Sala-mans fuhtja/ un likke Tramnu no Tirus atweſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Tas bija weenas Atrait-nes Dehts no tahs Zilts Nawta-li/ un winna Tehws bija weens Wihrs no Tirus biis/ weens Ammatneeks eekſch Warra Dar-ba/ kas peepildihts bija ar Gud-ribu/ un Sapraschanu/ un Sin-naschanu/ wiſſadu Warra Dar-bu darriht. Schis nahze pee to Kehnizu Salamann/ un ſtrah-daja wiſſu winna Darbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un wiſch darrija diwi Warra Stabbus/ weens Stabs bija aſtonpadeſmits Ohleſchu augsts/ un weens Auklis no di-wipadeſmits Ohlektim bija ap-kahrt abbejeem Stabbeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Wiſch darrija arridsan diwi Pohgas no Warra iſlee-tas/ us to Stabbu Wirs-Gallu likt/ peezns Ohlektis bija iſkat-ras Pohgas Augstums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un us tahm Pohgahm bija tahda Sapihſchana Eihla Darbá/ un Stibpas ta ka Schkehdes/ſeptinas bija tai wee-nat Pohgai/ un ſeptinas ohtrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Ta darrija wiſch tohs Stabbus/ un diwi RindasGra-nata- Abbotu pahr to Eihla Darbu avkahrt/ tahs Pohgas/ kas angſcham bija apfegt/ ta\n"
    }
